title: Make Your Own Easel Frames
description:
2 Simple Steps!

Choose your frame, then choose your easel boards!

Mix + Match any combination of boards.

Please note: Easel Boards are sold separately and can be found

here

.

Our ranges of Make Your Own indoor and outdoor easels are totally unique. They are the most versatile and flexible easel on the market and made to cater for the demands of everyday use in nurseries/schools.

Modular – Easel frames are modular so that you can easily configure 2 to 4 sided easels and a 6 sided option, as you require (for example your 4 sided easel can easily convert to two separate 2 sided easels).

One easel for all ages – Easel frames height is 1220mm – but each easel board is easily adjustable (with just one click) to suit the age and size of your children from as low as 100mm above ground (for younger children).

Choose from 2 types of 600 x 600mm easel board: Clear Perspex (indoor/outdoor) – ideal for painting and White Perspex (indoor/outdoor) – ideal for dry wipe markers as well as painting.

Paint pots not included. Suitable for paint pots 75mm.

Age

2+
